&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Human-Centric Threat Hunting Team Fights Cyber Attacks&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Threat hunting is an activity in which a team of experts use a multitude of technology tools and human intelligence to deeply assesses and analyze a &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.digitaljournal.com/pr/3267239&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.digitaljournal.com/pr/3267239&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

